<Author>freelancer
<Content>Great location Big fan of the Domus-have stayed there 3 times while visiting Berlin. Rooms are sparse; bed, TV,table and chairs but it is clean and in a great location within walking distance of the Ku'damm. Shower was a bit small and leaked alot which required some mopping up. Lots of good local restaurants in the neighbourhood. Very quiet-no noise from street.Breakfast is included and just fine. 
